txt.en: 'The Lumber-mill has been rebuilt, but there is much to do to get it fully functional and have it look like it belongs within our town. Bunks for the residents, crates and barrels for storage, and tools for the workers are all things that need to be added for the mill to begin full production.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
